overview: Sex crazed TS teens Chelsea Poe and Aspen Brooks babysit for pocket money - and to seduce all the sex-deprived new moms and dads. But when Chelsea's tryst with muscular dad Jaxton Wheeler destroys his marriage, the sexy redhead finds herself falling for his devastated, voluptuous wife (Susie Q). Meanwhile, beautiful brunette Aspen zeroes in on flustered single dad Ty Roderick until she meets his gorgeous brother Vadim Black.
tagline: The best babysitters play with Mommy and Daddy too
title: TS Babysitters
